  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402530/extras/97786714e4cc106932a774880e5badac.poster.avif?t=1760978092\" width=400 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402530/extras/97786714e4cc106932a774880e5badac.webm?t=1760978092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402530/extras/97786714e4cc106932a774880e5badac.mp4?t=1760978092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let a cozy kitty settle right on your desktop!<br>This is not just a virtual pet — it's your new furry companion who will live beside you while you work, study, or play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐾 <strong>11 unique cats to choose from</strong><br>Choose your perfect pet! From a striped mischief-maker to a fluffy aristocrat — there is a kitty for every taste.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🖥️ <strong>Free behavior</strong><br>The cat freely roams around your desktop, explores the screen, and interacts with you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍖 <strong>Care and maintenance</strong><br>Feed, pet, put to sleep, and play with your cat. Caring keeps it happy and active.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402530/extras/fe23de3499d2db4d800ee1e1d3afc435.poster.avif?t=1760978092\" width=400 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402530/extras/fe23de3499d2db4d800ee1e1d3afc435.webm?t=1760978092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402530/extras/fe23de3499d2db4d800ee1e1d3afc435.mp4?t=1760978092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💓 <strong>Purring adjustment</strong><br>Adjust the volume of purring to perfectly fit into your work rhythm.<br><br>🎮 <strong>Toys and entertainment</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place a <strong>scratching post</strong>, <strong>litter box</strong>, give a <strong>ball</strong> or a <strong>teaser stick</strong>. Watch how it interacts and entertains itself.<br><br>🌌 <strong>Exploring beyond the screen</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sometimes the cat goes \"beyond the screen\" — into its mysterious adventures.<br>It might return with <strong>rare collectible items</strong>, each with its own <strong>little story</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 <strong>Full customization</strong><br>Change the appearance of the cat, add hats, beds, new sounds.<br>Supports <strong>Steam Workshop</strong> — create and install mods!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402530/extras/70ccf2ed5c5ac93cc643336f3d808d38.poster.avif?t=1760978092\" width=400 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402530/extras/70ccf2ed5c5ac93cc643336f3d808d38.webm?t=1760978092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402530/extras/70ccf2ed5c5ac93cc643336f3d808d38.mp4?t=1760978092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402530/extras/97786714e4cc106932a774880e5badac.poster.avif?t=1760978092\" width=400 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402530/extras/97786714e4cc106932a774880e5badac.webm?t=1760978092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402530/extras/97786714e4cc106932a774880e5badac.mp4?t=1760978092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let a cozy kitty settle right on your desktop!<br>This is not just a virtual pet — it's your new furry companion who will live beside you while you work, study, or play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐾 <strong>11 unique cats to choose from</strong><br>Choose your perfect pet! From a striped mischief-maker to a fluffy aristocrat — there is a kitty for every taste.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🖥️ <strong>Free behavior</strong><br>The cat freely roams around your desktop, explores the screen, and interacts with you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍖 <strong>Care and maintenance</strong><br>Feed, pet, put to sleep, and play with your cat. Caring keeps it happy and active.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402530/extras/fe23de3499d2db4d800ee1e1d3afc435.poster.avif?t=1760978092\" width=400 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402530/extras/fe23de3499d2db4d800ee1e1d3afc435.webm?t=1760978092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402530/extras/fe23de3499d2db4d800ee1e1d3afc435.mp4?t=1760978092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💓 <strong>Purring adjustment</strong><br>Adjust the volume of purring to perfectly fit into your work rhythm.<br><br>🎮 <strong>Toys and entertainment</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place a <strong>scratching post</strong>, <strong>litter box</strong>, give a <strong>ball</strong> or a <strong>teaser stick</strong>. Watch how it interacts and entertains itself.<br><br>🌌 <strong>Exploring beyond the screen</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sometimes the cat goes \"beyond the screen\" — into its mysterious adventures.<br>It might return with <strong>rare collectible items</strong>, each with its own <strong>little story</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 <strong>Full customization</strong><br>Change the appearance of the cat, add hats, beds, new sounds.<br>Supports <strong>Steam Workshop</strong> — create and install mods!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402530/extras/70ccf2ed5c5ac93cc643336f3d808d38.poster.avif?t=1760978092\" width=400 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402530/extras/70ccf2ed5c5ac93cc643336f3d808d38.webm?t=1760978092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402530/extras/70ccf2ed5c5ac93cc643336f3d808d38.mp4?t=1760978092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
